{
  "texts": [
    "The training sensor label store holds the bounds for all seen actuation states.",
    "Once the testing actuation state is mapped to the training actuation state; the bounds are read out from the store. 3.",
    "Next, the testing sensor value at time t is verified against the bounds and an appropriate message is raised -depending on whether it is within or out of bounds.",
    "Any out of bound result further triggers a read out of the location of the sensor in X, Y, Z coordinates in the floor plan of the plant.",
    "The inverse mapping makes testing extremely fast and instantaneously points the operator to the anomalous sensor location."
  ]
}